.PP
\fBParameters:\fP
.RS 4
\fIcond\fP A condition variable object\&. 
.br
\fImtx\fP A mutex object\&. 
.br
\fIxt\fP A point in time at which the request will time out (absolute time)\&. 
.RE
.PP
